      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. For the second point about the capitalist structure, how should I handle the counter-arguments? Like, people always bring up \"meritocracy\" or the idea that people just work harder. Should I include those, or do they just kind of make the essay look weak if I give them too much space?",
